## 2. Create Your Expo Account

> 🔗 **Official Reference:** https://expo.dev/signup

### Step 2.1 — Register at expo.dev

1. Go to **https://expo.dev/signup**
2. Enter your **Full Name**, **Email**, and **Password** (min 8 chars)
3. Click **"Create Account"**
4. Verify your email via the confirmation link Expo sends

### Step 2.2 — Verify Your Email
- Check your inbox for a message from **noreply@expo.dev**
- Click **"Verify Email Address"**
- You'll be redirected to the Expo dashboard

### Step 2.3 — Explore the Expo Dashboard
After login at **https://expo.dev**, you have access to:

| Section | Purpose |
|---|---|
| **Projects** | View all your Expo apps |
| **Builds** | EAS Build history and artifacts |
| **Updates** | OTA update channels |
| **Submissions** | App store submission history |
| **Credentials** | Keystores, certificates, provisioning profiles |
| **Secrets** | Environment secrets for builds |

### Step 2.4 — Create an Organization (Optional but Recommended)
For team projects:
1. Dashboard → **Settings** → **Organizations** → **Create Organization**
2. Invite team members by email
> 🔗 https://docs.expo.dev/accounts/account-types/

